Good Alternate Resource

Shiny extension package:

1. https://github.com/daattali/colourpicker
2. https://github.com/dreamRs/shinyWidgets
3. https://rstudio.github.io/sortable/ : The sortable package enables drag-and-drop behaviour in your Shiny apps
4. https://github.com/nanxstats/awesome-shiny-extensions#desktop-deploy : You can find a comprehensive, actively-maintained list of other packages




